description:
Dennis came to me with a very interesting request.
"I'd like to get tied up," he said very matter-of-factly.
He said that he'd been thinking about it a lot and the idea of getting fucked while tied up was really starting to turn him on.
I thought it would be fun to give it a try!
When I asked Jonah if he was interested, he laughed.
"Yeah," he said. "I've done stuff like before, so, yeah I'd be down..."
title: Dennis & Jonah
